<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="ops-shell page-stack">
    <view class="card intro-card">
      <view class="page-title">业务维护</view>
      <view class="text-body">你好，{{displayName || '用户'}}。所有维护动作统一在这里执行，首页只承担经营盘面与提醒入口。</view>
      <view class="text-muted">维护入口固定：房源维护、租约维护。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="card action-card quick-card">
      <view class="section-head-main">
        <view class="section-title">房源维护</view>
        <view class="text-muted">用于新增和维护房源、房间基础信息，保证后续租约录入顺畅。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="action-buttons">
        <button class="primary-button" data-url="/pages/assets-form/index" bindtap="navigateTo">房源维护</button>
        <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="openUnitsTab">房源列表</button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card action-card">
      <view class="section-head-main">
        <view class="section-title">租约维护</view>
        <view class="text-muted">录入租约并查看租约清单，便于后续账单与提醒处理。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="ops-grid">
        <button class="secondary-button" data-url="/pages/leases-form/index" bindtap="navigateTo">租约录入</button>
        <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="openLeaseList">租约列表</button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card action-card export-card">
      <view class="section-head-main">
        <view class="section-title">月度经营导出</view>
        <view class="text-muted">按月份导出房租、水电、房东支出和退租支出明细。</view>
      </view>
      <button class="secondary-button" data-url="/pages/report-export/index" bindtap="navigateTo">月度经营导出</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
